          "correctOptionId": "opt-1",
          "explanation": "I 1st order reaction half life remains constant and clearence remains constant In zero order reaction half life decrease with decrease in concentration Ref:Guyton and Hall textbook of medical physiology 12th edition,page number:489,490"
