          "id": "medmcqa-d9339321-fa74-47df-ac54-74534194171e",
          "text": "A patient presents to emergency with pinpoint pupil, salivation, lacrimation, tremors and red tears. Plasma cholinesterase level was 30% of normal. Most probable Diagnosis is:",
