          "id": "medmcqa-dd18aa21-d143-4473-9bf9-65f67be5534e",
          "text": "A diabetic patient developed cellulitis due to Staphylococcus aureus, which was found to be Methicillin resistant on the antibiotic sensitivity testing. All the following antibiotics will be appropriate except:",
