          "id": "medmcqa-69ccc4e3-9e53-45e6-9c64-a8071be4a348",
          "text": "Roopa Devi, a 65-year-old female with lymph-node-positive breast cancer was treated with systemic chemotherapy. Four weeks later, she developed frequent urination, suprapubic pain, dysuria, and hematuria. Which of the following could have prevented this patient's condition?",
